Task
Change the sign of a number
A number is given. Get the inverse of the given one.
Write a function called oppositeNumber that takes num as an argument and returns the opposite number.
Example:
• function oppositeNumber (9) must return -9;
• the oppositeNumber (-7) function must return 7;
• the oppositeNumber (0) function must return 0.

Solution
function oppositeNumber (num) {
return -num;
}
